&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;7+ years of full-cycle technical recruiting experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2+ years focused on Product or Design recruiting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A track record of building your own pipelines and shaping sourcing strategies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep familiarity with Product and/or Design communities and the latest trends in tech&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven success partnering with leaders to navigate complex offers to close top candidates&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience hiring exceptional technical talent at a high-growth startup or leading tech company&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
