&lt;li&gt;Used Figma’s products&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A team-first mindset—you live by “lift your team” and love learning from your peers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Gem and Greenhouse&lt;/li&gt;
