&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;308&quot; data-end=&quot;429&quot;&gt;
&lt;div data-start=&quot;310&quot; data-end=&quot;429&quot;&gt;Develop multi-agent communication and orchestration frameworks to enable collaboration and autonomous task execution&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;430&quot; data-end=&quot;563&quot;&gt;
&lt;div data-start=&quot;432&quot; data-end=&quot;563&quot;&gt;Partner with Finance, HR, Sales, Engineering, and IT to identify and deliver high-impact opportunities for AI-powered automation&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
